<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Jun1923"><font color="red">10 June 1923</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): My small flat is all upside down with ten cases of books and manuscripts, three sacks of newspapers, four trunks, four valises, three hatboxes etc. I expect to leave Paris on Saturday (16 June 1923) &hellip; As regards the sight it seems to be getting very slowly better. I can now do some reading and have raced through many accumulated books and notes. </div>
